stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> nuevo : Primera DM recibida\nINSERT INTO leads\nscore = 0–25

    %% ─── FROM NUEVO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    nuevo --> caliente : purchase keywords detected\nOR interest_strong intent\nFollower asks about price/product\nscore → 45–85

    nuevo --> colaborador : collaboration keywords ≥ 2\n('collab', 'partnership', 'mención')\nscore → 30–60

    nuevo --> amigo : bidirectional social exchange\nboth sides: social keywords\nscore → 15–45

    nuevo --> frío : inactive 14+ days\nsince last message\nscore → 0–10

    %% ─── FROM CALIENTE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    caliente --> cliente : Payment webhook received\nStripe/Hotmart/PayPal\n[PERMANENT — never downgraded]\nscore → 75–100

    caliente --> frío : inactive 14+ days\nno purchase confirmed\nscore → 0–10

    caliente --> nuevo : signals drop\nno purchase intent\nscore → 0–25

    %% ─── FROM FRÍO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    frío --> caliente : Re-engagement\nnew purchase-intent DM\nscore → 45–85

    frío --> nuevo : Re-engagement\ngeneral new DM (low signal)\nscore → 0–25

    %% ─── FROM COLABORADOR ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    colaborador --> caliente : shifts to buying intent\npurchase keywords appear\nscore → 45–85

    colaborador --> amigo : social pattern dominates\nscore → 15–45

    %% ─── FROM AMIGO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    amigo --> caliente : purchase intent emerges\nscore → 45–85

    amigo --> frío : inactive 14+ days\nscore → 0–10

    %% ─── CLIENTE IS PERMANENT ────────────────────────────────────────────────
    cliente --> cliente : status PRESERVED\nall future rescores keep cliente\nonly score updates (75–100)

    note right of cliente
        PROTECTED STATUS:
        classify_lead() checks
        existing status first.
        cliente → NEVER downgraded.
        Payment webhook is the
        ONLY entry point.
    end note

    note right of frío
        GHOST REACTIVATION:
        Scheduler detects frío leads
        that were previously caliente.
        Triggers re-engagement DM
        via nurturing engine.
        services/nurturing_service.py
    end note

    note right of nuevo
        LEAD SCORING ALGORITHM (V3):

        Step 1: extract_signals()
          • purchase_keywords (follower msgs only)
          • interest_keywords
          • social_keywords
          • collaboration_keywords
          • bidirectional_ratio
          • days_since_last_contact
          • total_messages

        Step 2: classify_lead()
          Priority order:
          1. cliente (preserved)
          2. caliente (purchase ≥1 + interest ≥1)
          3. colaborador (collab ≥2)
          4. amigo (social both sides)
          5. frío (inactive ≥14d + history)
          6. nuevo (default)

        Step 3: calculate_score()
          Range per category:
          cliente:     75–100
          caliente:    45–85
          colaborador: 30–60
          amigo:       15–45
          nuevo:        0–25
          frío:         0–10
    end note
